# Mailbox
IMAPStore mailbox-remote
Host imap.mailbox.org
Port 993
UserCmd "pass show mail/mailbox | awk '$1 == \"user:\" {print $2}'"
PassCmd "pass show mail/mailbox | awk '$1 == \"apppwd:\" {print $2}'"
TLSType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN PLAIN
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore mailbox-local
Path ~/.local/share/isync/mailbox/
Inbox ~/.local/share/isync/mailbox/INBOX
Subfolders Verbatim

Channel mailbox
Far :mailbox-remote:
Near :mailbox-local:
Create Both
Expunge Both
Patterns *
SyncState *

# TUW
IMAPStore tuw-remote
Host mail.intern.tuwien.ac.at
Port 993
UserCmd "pass show tuw/mail | awk '$1 == \"user2:\" {print $2}'"
PassCmd "pass show tuw/mail | head -n1"
TLSType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN PLAIN
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore tuw-local
Path ~/.local/share/isync/tuw/
Inbox ~/.local/share/isync/tuw/INBOX
Subfolders Verbatim

Channel tuw
Far :tuw-remote:
Near :tuw-local:
Create Both
Expunge Both
Patterns *
SyncState *
